Package: nimix
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Mixture Clustering and Regression with NIMBLE
Version: 0.4.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Achmad", "Syyahrul Choir", email = "madsyair@stis.ac.id", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Bayesian finite and nonparametric mixture modelling built on top of
    the 'nimble' package. This 0.3.0 release provides the S4 architecture
    foundation, univariate and multivariate Gaussian mixture clustering, and a
    Dirichlet Process Mixture of linear regressions, all using a DPM engine via
    the Chinese Restaurant Process (de Valpine et al. 2017
    <doi:10.1080/10618600.2016.1172487>; Neal 2000
    <doi:10.1080/10618600.2000.10474879>; Zhang et al. 2004
    <doi:10.1023/B:STCO.0000039481.32735.0c>; Hurn et al. 2003
    <doi:10.1198/1061860031329>). Post-hoc label switching correction wraps the
    'label.switching' package (Papastamoulis 2016 <doi:10.18637/jss.v069.c01>).
    A reversible jump MCMC engine is planned for a later release.
License: GPL-3
